title: Far East Taco Grille
typeOfFood: Lacto, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Asian Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little eatery making Asian fusion with Korean and Mexican flavors in taco, burrito, and bowl format - all the styles can be requested vegan with tofu and minus mayonaise and dairy (crema sauce, sour cream, cheese). Its food truck roams around Washington DC.
